@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state InitialState
InitialState : entry / User logs in or system starts

[*] --> InitialState : Start event

InitialState --> ServiceCenterHome : Login or Startup event
ServiceCenterHome : entry / Logged in Service Center
ServiceCenterHome : do / Display home page
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Enter Damaged parts list
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Expiry Notification page
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Updating Information list
ServiceCenterHome --> JourneyDetails : User selects destination
JourneyDetails : entry / User views journey details
JourneyDetails : do / Display journey details
JourneyDetails : exit / Activate driving mode or choose other options
JourneyDetails --> EatSelection : User is hungry
EatSelection : entry / User selects a place to eat
EatSelection : do / View menu and place order if necessary
EatSelection : exit / Return to JourneyDetails
ServiceCenterHome --> AccidentReporting : Accident occurs
AccidentReporting : entry / System informs relevant authorities
AccidentReporting : do / Send notifications during driving or in case of an accident
AccidentReporting : exit / Return to ServiceCenterHome
JourneyDetails --> Feedback : User completes journey
Feedback : entry / User provides feedback
Feedback : do / Allow users to provide feedback
Feedback : exit / Logout or return to JourneyDetails
ServiceCenterHome --> Logout : User logs out
Logout : entry / To Logout
Logout : do / Logout
Logout : exit / Logged out Successfully

state ExpiryNotification
ExpiryNotification : entry / To view expiry notification
ExpiryNotification : do / Send service request to Car owner
ExpiryNotification : exit / Return to Service center home page
ExpiryNotification --> ServiceCenterHome : Service request sent event

state Entering Damaged parts list
Entering Damaged parts list : entry / To enter Damaged parts list
Entering Damaged parts list : do / Preparing and entering damaged parts list
Entering Damaged parts list : exit / Return to service center home page
Entering Damaged parts list --> ServiceCenterHome : Damaged parts entered event

state Updating parts Information
Updating parts Information : entry / To update changed parts information
Updating parts Information : do / Update Information
Updating parts Information : exit / Return to Service center home page
Updating parts Information --> ServiceCenterHome : Parts updated event

ServiceCenterHome --> TerminalState : Completion event
TerminalState : entry / System has completed all tasks
TerminalState : do / No operation
TerminalState : exit / End of the system run
@enduml
